sentence: i need a flight from san diego california to indianapolis indiana leaving in the afternoon on tuesday
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.flight_id||'"', v0.departure_time, '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v3.state_code||'"', '"'||v3.state_name||'"',
 '"'||v4.airport_code||'"', '"'||v5.city_code||'"', '"'||v5.city_name||'"',

 '"'||v7.days_code||'"', '"'||v8.day_name||'"', v8.year,
 v8.month_number, v8.day_number FROM flight v0, airport_service v1,
 city v2, state v3, airport_service v4, city v5,
 state v6, days v7, date_day v8

AND ((v0.flight_days = ANY v7.days_code) AND ((v7.day_name = ANY v8.day_name)
